702149f-a.text:
White Plains Road, at Burke Ave., showing the elevated station of the I.R.T. White Plains Road subway line. The frame houses, seen on the right, are west of White Plains Road on the south side of Burke Ave., extending from White Plains Road to Olinville Ave.
About 1917.
James Suydam.
